Stay in the Heart of Barcelona – Excellent location – show map

One of our best sellers in Barcelona! Paseo de Gracia Bas Apartments Barcelona is centrally located, just an 8-minute walk from Plaza Catalunya and Las Ramblas. It features air-conditioned apartments with free Wi-Fi and smart TVs with internet connection.

Furnished with hardwood floors, each apartment features a modern and functional décor. Apartments have a pleasant lounge area with a sofa and floor-to-ceiling windows. The kitchens include a dishwasher, microwave and coffee machine. There is also a Smart TV with a keyboard and internet access. The bathroom includes a hydro-massage shower.

Paseo de Gracia Bas Apartments are surrounded by a wide range of bars, traditional Spanish restaurants, as well as shops and supermarkets. Las Ramblas, Plaza Catalunya Square, and the Gothic Quarter are all approximately a 10-minute walk away.

The apartments are just a 3-minute walk from the fashionable Paseo de Gracia Avenue. Gaudí's masterpiece Casa Batlló is a quarter mile away. Guests can go to the beach by car or with public transportation in less than 10 minutes from the apartments.

Regular airport buses to Barcelona El Prat Airport leave from a bus stop in Plaza Catalunya. Guests can also catch a train to the airport from nearby Passeig de Gràcia Train Station.

Eixample is a great choice for travelers interested in architecture, food and city walks.

This is our guests' favorite part of Barcelona, according to independent reviews.

This property also has one of the top-rated locations in Barcelona! Guests are happier about it compared to other properties in the area.

Couples in particular like the location – they rated it 9.8 for a two-person trip.

This property is also rated for the best value in Barcelona! Guests are getting more for their money when compared to other properties in this city.

Hosted by Paseo de Gracia Bas Apartments Barcelona

Host Review Score 9.5

Paseo de Gracia Bas Apartments Barcelona

Paseo de Gracia Bas Apartments Barcelona is centrally located. These spacious, modern apartments feature wooden floors and have a living room with a sofa and a Smart TV, which you can use to access the Internet and Skype. High Speed Wi-FI is offered free of charge. Our beds have memory foam mattresses and pillows that ensure a great comfort to our guests. A safe box is available in the main bedroom. The bed linen and the towels are included in the price of the apartment. Besides, the extra cleaning service is offered every two nights. The bathroom is equipped with a hydro massage shower with 5 different modes. Some of the apartments have a terrace with some pieces of furniture: a good option to relax after a long day shopping and sightseeing. Our kitchen is fully equipped so the guests can prepare their own meals. We have all the necessary elements like dish-washer (with detergent included), washing machine (with detergent pods included), microwave, oven, gas stove, fridge, freezer, dishes, cutlery, cups, glasses, fry pans and pots. We include olive oil and salt to ease the meal preparation.

The apartments are just 1 minute walk from Paseo de Gracia Avenue. A place where you can find the fanciest shops in Barcelona, a large variety of restaurants and two Gaudi’s masterpieces: Casa Batlló and la Pedrera. Public transportation can be used to reach other districts of Barcelona. The guest can choose among a large variety of transports like buses, taxis, bike rentals, metro, train and FGC lines. There is also a Touristic Bus stop at Plaça de Catalunya. Las Ramblas, Plaza Catalunya Square, and the Gothic Quarter are all approximately a 10-minute walk away.

Languages spoken: Catalan, English, Spanish, French, Italian, Russian
